These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, project-manager
1. the accountant is in an even position##4
2. the project-manager is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks |
| Job     | project-manager    | accountant   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | tea | water        |
| Sport      | surfing  | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, pakistani
1. the colombian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | gospel |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, banana
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | fanta      | iced-tea |
| Food       | strawberry | banana    |

 #################################

 
